2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Sport   | swimming | soccer | volleyball | water-polo |

 